    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Settlements of any kind with defensive structures such as moats, enclosures, or ramparts. Fortification became necessary from the Neolithic period onward, as people began to settle in one place.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
